This paper discusses the challenges and solutions for managing massive machine-type communications (MTC) over LTE/LTE-A networks, which are related to network infrastructure, information theory, system engineering, multimedia, and cryptography. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
